<p>In my OS X app, I create a NSButton (for configure purpose) with NSImagetemplate(NSImageNameActionTemplate) and I want to apply tint color(ex. blue like Xcode).</p>  <p>but I can not change the NSImagetemplate's color. How to apply a tint color for my configure button?</p>  <p>the below code is about the creation of my configuration button.</p>  <pre><code>    configurationButton = NSButton(frame: NSMakeRect(0, 0, 50, 50))     configurationButton.image = NSImage(named: NSImageNameActionTemplate)     configurationButton.bordered = false     configurationButton.setButtonType(NSButtonType.MomentaryChangeButton) </code></pre>